  - continuous performance test
  - computational psychiatry
  - open data
abstract: >
  An independent, exploratory re-analysis of two open ADHD datasets (HYPERAKTIV, BALLADEER)
  testing a hypothesized behavioral subtype structure. Finds replicated evidence for
  impulsivity heterogeneity in ADHD relative to neurotypical controls; does not find
  support for a hypothesized temporal (within-task) divergence between subtypes.
  Not peer-reviewed.
